To start a fight:

Make sure the following line is added to the erlang_config.rb of the relevant project:

ERL_FLAGS="-setcookie 'BRUATIZUOMNAIXZGHHNJ' -name 'dscore@dividedspace'"
or 
ERL_FLAGS="-setcookie 'BRUATIZUOMNAIXZGHHNJ' -name 'epic@dividedspace'"


Compile erlv8:
cd epic/lib/erlv8; make

Start the core app:
cd core; rake shell
dscore@dividedspace> center:start().

Start an Epic Server:
cd epic; rake shell
epic@dividedspace> epic:start().


Back on the dscore shell:
dscore@dividedspace> center:start_fight(1).

